 als auch in DLM-Daten größtenteils, wobei es in OSM etwas kompletter scheint. Außerdem wird deutlich, dass das Attribut zwischen den Datensätzen eine hohe Übereinstimmung aufweist. Generell lassen sich anhand der Übereinstimmung nicht direkt Rückschlüsse auf die Datenqualität schließen. Häufige Unterschiede im Attribut “lanes” sind\nbeispielsweise stark durch unterschiedliche Kartierungsregeln geprägt.","position":{"start":{"line":58,"column":1},"end":{"line":58,"column":1}},"key":"FQ7XEan7X4"}],"key":"HY8lmYheZy"},{"type":"div","children":[{"type":"image","url":"/oqapi-jupyter-book/build/Road_accuracy_name_H-20177a118b2464de269d2d875daa7b0e.png","width":600,"key":"NgAwi4s22r","urlSource":"../abbildungen/Road_accuracy_name_HD.png"}],"key":"qnz5Xx3ewv"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":1},"end":{"line":68,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Referenzen","position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":1},"end":{"line":68,"column":1}},"key":"oB4GkAmBvw"}],"identifier":"referenzen","label":"Referenzen","html_id":"referenzen","implicit":true,"key":"ZuBI1Ghucn"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":70,"column":1},"end":{"line":70,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":70,"column":1},"end":{"line":70,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"A. Wöltche, “Open source map matching with Markov decision processes: A new method and a detailed benchmark with existing approaches”, Transactions in GIS, vol. 27, no. 7, pp. 1959–1991, Oct. 2023, doi: ","position":{"start":{"line":70,"column":1},"end":{"line":70,"column":1}},"key":"PGiTupWxoW"},{"type":"cite","url":"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1111/tgis.13107","position":{"start":{"line":70,"column":1},"end":{"line":70,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wöltche (2023)","key":"dM5O9BSdR6"}],"kind":"narrative","label":"W_ltche_2023","identifier":